They have a seance, and Sue claims to see the Santa Maria sail across the family room wall after trying to awaken the spirit of Christopher Columbus. Brick goes to a Halloween party dressed as a bookmark, where he has an accident and gets a concussion. He then requires his parents to look at his eyes every hours. With the help of the rest of his family, Brick asks out a girl he's enamored with, using social media.

data: Several villages wiped out and the throats of men slit in front of their wives and children.
Students suspected of being members of the ELF were hanged in the centre of town. Parents of the slain were forced, by the Ethiopian Army, to unhang their dead children and take them home.
The village elders were rounded up for supporting the Eritrean Liberation Front and killed.
The entire village was rounded up into the local mosque and the mosque's doors were locked, the building was then razed and survivors were shot.
Ethiopian Army units surrounded the village killing civilians and burning down the village.
Students were strangled to death using piano wires, their bodies were dumped in alleyways and doorsteps.
Students and youth suspected of supporting the ELF were publicly executed by hanging. Family members were forced to attend the execution and cut down their children from the noose.
Shortly after an EPLF attack on two Ethiopian divisions, Ethiopian troops fire upon civilians gathered in Churches, homes and schools.
During an engagement with the EPLF and ELF the Ethiopian Army attacked the church where villagers had taken refuge.
After several ELF attacks on the town the Ethiopian Army retaliated on the local population.
The villagers were machine gunned in front of a river to prevent escape.
The dead were mostly women and children as the men had moved to the towns to eke out a living for their impoverished village.
